content: इषि(षी)का [इष् गत्यादौ क्वुन् अत इत्वं] {@--1@} Reed, rush, stalk of grass; कुशकाशशरेषिकाः <ls>Rām.</ls>; °अस्त्रं <ls>R. 12. 23.</ls> {@--2@} An arrow. {@--3@} A sort of sugar-cane; Saccharum Spontaneum. {@--4@} A small stick of wood or iron used to see whether gold in a crucible is melted or not. {@--5@} A brush. {@--6@} The eye ball of an elephant.
